      <title>欧盟贷款部门承诺加快乌克兰支出</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/eus-lending-arm-pledges-speed-up-ukraine-spending-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟的贷款机构欧洲投资银行(EIB)已签署承诺，将加速使用今年准备支持乌克兰重建工作的超过5.6亿欧元（5.959亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/eus-lending-arm-pledges-speed-up-ukraine-spending-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 21:38:23 GMT</pubDate>
