      <title>独家：消息人士称，摩根大通交易撮合者利普斯基和李将离开该行</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-dealmakers-lipsky-lee-are-leaving-bank-sources-say-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两位知情人士周四表示，摩根大通的两名高级交易撮合者安迪·利普斯基 (Andy Lipsky) 和海迪·李 (Haidee Lee) 将离开该行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-dealmakers-lipsky-lee-are-leaving-bank-sources-say-2024-04-18/</guid>
